# Astro Components

- Use `getLangFromUrl(Astro.url)` and `useTranslations(lang)` for i18n
- Reference translation keys from data files, never hardcode user-facing strings
- Use design token classes (`bg-bg`, `text-brand`, `bg-surface`) — no raw hex values
- Headings use `font-inter`, body text uses `font-satoshi`
- Add `id` attributes to sections for nav anchor links
- Only use Svelte (`.svelte`) for components that need client-side interactivity

```astro
---
import { getLangFromUrl, useTranslations } from "@/lib/i18n";
const lang = getLangFromUrl(Astro.url);
const t = useTranslations(lang);
---
<section id="example">
  <h2 class="font-inter font-black text-text-primary">{t("section.title")}</h2>
</section>
```
